            <p style="color: white; font-family: 'Mochiy Pop P One', sans-serif;">This project is based around Charlottenlund VGS and collects weather and Buss Information from its location</p>
            <p style="color: white; font-family: 'Mochiy Pop P One', sans-serif;">You can change this configuration in the .env file</p>
            <br>
