            <p style="color: white; font-family: 'Mochiy Pop P One', sans-serif;">After you are done. Set INSTALLED=TRUE in the .env file and restart the Node.JS server</p>

            <p style="color: white; font-family: 'Mochiy Pop P One', sans-serif;">IMPORTANT: The URL needs to be correct, or the callback wil not work from Auth0 and Spotify. (It is by default set to localhost)</p>
